{
  "stem": "16214.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And because I was like a pioneer, you know, and-- and the thing is that you are a leader of the pioneers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because you happen to be a good student, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So this has nothing to do with your choice of, you know, whatnot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I did finally-- was able to get out of Israel, within like maybe 24 hours of my-- either you-- you go to Israel or to the military, because the military was after me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they gave me also a limited time of getting out of Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was really upset.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't want to come to United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But, now I'm glad I-- I did come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was-- it wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I did not speak English, again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so going from one country to another, I had to learn a new language, and new customs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was another shocking experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the most wonderful experience was that my parents, unlike what people were telling me in Israel, they were delighted, you know, to-- for me to just go straight back to school.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And not only that, but they insisted on that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was very happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I remember my mother, and the whole family almost came to Idlewild Airport at that time to pick me up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my sister grew so much in one year that I could hardly-- I didn't recognize her even.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were standing upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I did not see anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the lady who was the stewardess was my girlfriend, and I knew all the pilots.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one pilot was holding one of my valises.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Little-- I had very, very little packages, just little valises.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because everybody said you're going to the United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You won't need anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
